<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-50-0243 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper describes experience of greenhouse construction on the roofsof buildings and their heating design with the use of secondary energyresources, particularly the vent air exhausted from a building. Thisair warms the cold internal surface of the glazing and compensates forthe heat losses in the greenhouse before being rejected to the surroundings.</TEXT></DOC>